  "description": "A close-up, high-angle shot of the vibrant green leaves of a flax plant (Harakeke in M\u0101ori). The leaves are long, slender, and arch upwards, creating a dense, textured pattern. Sunlight filters through the leaves, creating bright highlights and deep shadows, enhancing the depth and three-dimensionality of the image. The plant appears healthy and lush, with a natural and organic feel. The composition focuses on the central rosette of leaves, with some leaves slightly blurred in the background. It presents a strong sense of botanical detail and natural beauty.",
